As an established entertainment company, we write “entertainment” in capitals. Moreover, we know how to select the best speakers, athletes, celebrities, spokespersons or artists for your event, seminar or function. Ffor years, we’ve booked the world&#8217;s most renowned names for private and corporate events. From international artists to soccer players, movie stars, inspiring and leading entrepreneurs, to the world&#8217;s number-one DJ’s or leaders of the state.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify"><img class="size-full wp-image-91 aligncenter" src="../wp-content/uploads/sites/852/2016/11/blog3.jpg" alt="about" width="800" height="459" srcset="../wp-content/uploads/sites/852/2016/11/blog3.jpg 800w, ../wp-content/uploads/sites/852/2016/11/blog3-300x172.jpg 300w, ../wp-content/uploads/sites/852/2016/11/blog3-768x441.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify"><strong>We create memories that will last a lifetime</strong><br />
Whilst doing serious business, entertainment is a welcome breath of fresh air. Our aim is to help you create everlasting memories by finding the perfect celebrity. Being one of the worlds’ premier booking agencies, we will take care of all necessary arrangements. From booking to contracting. We will also advise you about logistics, riders as well as technical production. We can see to travel-schedules, moreover we can look after all necessary arrangements, permits and scheduling on location.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify"><strong>Entertainment and more…</strong><br />
Keeping you care-free is our commitment. We can provide technical production, logistic management or full service event-management.<br />
We’ll be more than happy to assist you with:<br />
&#8211; pre-production<br />
&#8211; event coordination<br />
&#8211; fstage, sound, lighting, backline and technical facilities<br />
&#8211; artist riders<br />
&#8211; security staff<br />
&#8211; itineraries: flight grids, hotels, VIP transport<br />
&#8211; meet &amp; greets and photo-opps</p>
<p style="text-align: justify"><strong>Dedication</strong><br />
Commitment and quality are our key words to achieve the best experience for your guests and customers. These successes encourage our customers to return to us constantly. With years of experience, we assure you a successful corporate event, private concert, campaign or press-presentation.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify"><strong>Worldwide experience</strong><br />
We don’t just book celebrities. We create memories that will last a lifetime.<br />
As we work for multinationals, corporations and high profile clients all over the world, we are accustomed to perform at high standards. EBA offers you total support when booking<br />
celebrities for your event, endorsement or performance.</p>
